ESCAPE: Close
WASD: Move camera forward/backward/right/left
QZ: Move camera up/down
G: toggle wireframe
U: update waves
E: generate waves
O/^O: raise/lower min amplitude
M/^M: raise/lower max amplitude
R: raise/lower roughness
T: raise/lower wavelength
L: lod level
N: grid level
V: max_distance
P: print camera position/direction
F: display fps
UP/DOWN/LEFT/RIGHT: move light
RIGHT BRACKET/LEFT BRACKET: change camera speed